List all bluetooth adapters:listblue_ph.sh | more
List all Controller options:confopts_ph.sh -p list -a Controllers | more
Change a Controller option:confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Controllers -s
Change all Controller options:confopts_ph.sh -p set -a Controllers | more
Reset a Controller option:confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Controllers -r
Reset all Controller options:confopts_ph.sh -p reset -a Controllers | more
Display help for Controller options:confopts_ph.sh -p prompt -a Controllers -d
Go to Controllers:ph_show_menu Controllers
Go to Main:ph_show_menu Main
Open a shell (Type CTRL-D to return):echo;cd;/bin/bash
Quit:break
Return to previous screen:return
